Create an image of a Magic The Gathering card featuring "Chuckles," an Ape Pirate creature. Depict a mischievous, medium-sized ape wearing a pirate hat and tattered sash, standing on the deck of a ship, grinning widely. The ape is nimble and agile, surrounded by the open sea under a bright sky. The style is simple and straightforward, focusing on the fun, playful energy of the character rather than embellishments or dramatic effects.